<LP>
   BUFFALO, N.Y. -- Integrated Waste Services Inc. said it
acquired Southwestern Environmental and Wizard Method Inc.,
both of Niagara Falls, N.Y. Terms weren't disclosed.
   The waste-management company said it would merge the two
acquisitions into a wholly owned subsidiary. Southwestern
Environmental is a demolition and asbestos abatement
contractor, and Wizard Method is an industrial cleaning and
asbestos abatement concern.
</LP>
